---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import WhatsAppFloat from '../components/WhatsAppFloat.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ — Arepas With Friends" description="Preguntas frecuentes sobre la experiencia de arepas venezolanas.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <!-- Hero banner -->
    <div class="bg-marron py-16 px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-arepa-light mb-4">
        <span class="i18n-es">Preguntas frecuentes</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
      </h1>
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 hover:text-arepa-light transition-colors text-sm">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
        <span class="i18n-es">Volver al inicio</span>
        <span class="i18n-en">Back to home</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ items -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- Q1 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Cuánto dura la experiencia?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">How long is the experience?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">La experiencia tiene una duración total de 3 horas. En caso de requerir más tiempo, coordinarlo durante la reserva.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">The experience lasts a total of 3 hours. If more time is needed, arrange it during booking.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Para cuántas personas es?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">How many people is it for?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">Está pensada para grupos entre 4 y 10 personas.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">It is designed for groups of 4 to 10 people.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Dónde se realiza la experiencia?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">Where does the experience take place?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">Sugerimos realizarlo en nuestro espacio, el cual cuenta con las comodidades y está pensado para disfrutar por completo la experiencia. Sin embargo, podemos ir a tu domicilio.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">We suggest having it at our space, which has all the amenities and is designed to fully enjoy the experience. However, we can come to your place.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q4 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Cómo funciona la experiencia a domicilio?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">How does the at-home experience work?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">Nosotros llevamos todos los materiales e ingredientes necesarios para la elaboración de las arepas. Solo necesitamos una cocina disponible para preparar las arepas y vajilla completa acorde a la cantidad de personas. Para más detalles, condiciones y disponibilidad, consultanos por privado vía WhatsApp.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">We bring all the materials and ingredients needed for making the arepas. We just need an available kitchen to prepare the arepas and complete tableware for the number of people. For more details, conditions, and availability, contact us privately via WhatsApp.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q5 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Qué incluye la experiencia?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">What's included in the experience?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">Participación completa en la elaboración, degustación de arepas con distintos rellenos previamente preparados y 1 bebida sin alcohol individual por persona. Pero tenemos a la venta variedad de bebidas adicionales. Consultar al momento de la reserva.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Full participation in the preparation, tasting of arepas with different pre-prepared fillings, and 1 individual non-alcoholic drink per person. We also have a variety of additional drinks for sale. Ask at the time of booking.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q6 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Necesito saber cocinar?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">Do I need to know how to cook?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">No, está pensado para que cualquiera pueda participar y disfrutar.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">No, it is designed so anyone can participate and enjoy.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>

        <!-- Q7 -->
        <div class="faq-item bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-crema-dark/50 overflow-hidden">
          <details>
            <summary>
              <span class="flex-1 text-left">
                <span class="i18n-es">¿Cómo se reserva?</span>
                <span class="i18n-en">How do I book?</span>
              </span>
            </summary>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <span class="i18n-es">La reserva de fecha se realiza exclusivamente por WhatsApp. Escribinos indicando cantidad de personas y fecha deseada.</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Date booking is done exclusively via WhatsApp. Message us indicating number of people and desired date.</span>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA at bottom -->
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <p class="text-marron-light mb-6">
          <span class="i18n-es">¿Tenés más preguntas? Escribinos directamente.</span>
          <span class="i18n-en">Have more questions? Message us directly.</span>
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-whatsapp wa-link">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
          <span class="i18n-es">Reservar por WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="i18n-en">Book via WhatsApp</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
  <WhatsAppFloat />
</Layout>
